Text: Pinnacle is quickly approaching Remember all EES employees are eligible to be nominated but only those who stand out as top performers in their field will be selected for participation Pinnacle will be held at a fivestar resort on the island of Nevis in the West Indies This years event will be an exciting and great experience for those selected Click on the attachment below to get a feel of whats to come at Pinnacle After launching the file the Pinnacle website can be accessed by clicking on the link at the bottom of the page
